 In its heyday , Kejonuma Leisure Land , in Tohoku , Japan , attracted hundreds of thousands of visitors .
With an amusement park , campsite and driving range , the once-bustling family-friendly attraction closed its doors officially in 2000 following a drop in visitors .
Urban explorer Florian Seidel , 38 , visited the site in 2014 to capture the park 's ongoing dereliction .